Four Nuclear Units at Japanese Plant Have Sustained Core Damage, IAEA Says

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   P u r v i s   a n d   J o n a t h a n   T i r o n e
-- 
2011-03-16T15:49:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/four-nuclear-units-at-japanese-plant-have-sustained-core-damage-iaea-says.html
Four nuclear units in Japan have
core damage, the  International Atomic Energy Agency  said 
today in Vienna. Director General Yukiya Amano will travel to
Japan, the agency said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
